= Release 384 \(3 Jun 2022\)

== General

- Fix potential query failure due to a regression introduced in version 383. \(#issue("12667", "https://github.com/trinodb/trino/issues/12667")\)
- Fix potential failure or incorrect result of the #raw("json_query") #link(label("doc-functions-json"))[JSON function]. \(#issue("12681", "https://github.com/trinodb/trino/issues/12681")\)

